{"title":"秋日特辑 | 去川西，去最接近天堂的地方","uid":"74544a5b5216c424c5b8f8e62fd899f7","slug":"推文13","date":"2021-11-07T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-03-03T16:35:22.547Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/推文13.json","keywords":null,"cover":"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000524351.png","content":"<p><strong>横断山脉</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000407805.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000407805\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000447455.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000447455\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000452060.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000452060\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"阿坝：童话世界\"><a href=\"#阿坝：童话世界\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"阿坝：童话世界\"></a>阿坝：童话世界</h2><p>为“世界生态旅游最佳目的地”的阿坝州平日里，我们在成都遥望四姑娘山。</p>\n<p>这次，我们翻过巴朗山，越过垭口亲自站在了她的脚下。在猫鼻梁伫足望去，四座并排的山峰就像四位头戴纱巾的姑娘：</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000507842.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000507842\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000512606.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000512606\"></p>\n<p>四姑娘山景区由双桥沟、长坪沟、海子沟组成<br>其中以双桥沟的景色最为迷人</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000520203.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000520203\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000524351.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000524351\"></p>\n<p>白塔与彩林</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000533266.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000533266\"></p>\n<p>四姑娘山的另一面即是观赏彩林的绝佳胜地毕棚沟<br>每到十月毕棚沟的彩林从谷底绵延到山巅在阳光的照耀下显得光彩熠熠</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304000537482.png\" alt=\"image-20220304000537482\"></p>\n<p>姑娘山的另一面即是观赏彩林的绝佳胜地毕棚沟，每到十月毕棚沟的彩林从谷底绵延到山巅在阳光的照耀下显得光彩熠熠。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003143842.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003143842\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003150507.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003150507\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003154430.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003154430\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003159805.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003159805\"></p>\n<p>黄河这条中华民族的母亲河从青海发源一路向东在这里拐出了九曲黄河第一弯。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003213536.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003213536\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003218372.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003218372\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"甘孜：自驾天堂\"><a href=\"#甘孜：自驾天堂\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"甘孜：自驾天堂\"></a>甘孜：自驾天堂</h2><p>之城康定<br>在这里318国道即将开始它最美的行程</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003240865.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003240865\"></p>\n<p>第一座大山海拔4298米的折多山</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003248988.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003248988\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003253763.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003253763\"></p>\n<p>都桥最美的风景不在新都桥镇，而是在新都桥前往塔公草原的路上；秋天的G248公路是名副其实的“十里画廊”。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003314720.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003314720\"></p>\n<p>阳光下的胡杨林</p>\n<p>成群结队的牛羊</p>\n<p>星罗棋布的藏族村落</p>\n<p>再快的生活在这里都放慢了脚步</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003322722.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003322722\"></p>\n<p>被藏民奉为神山的雅拉雪山：</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003342544.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003342544\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003349921.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003349921\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003353069.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003353069\"></p>\n<p>古时期的海底岩石经地壳运动被抬升出来经过强大的地应力挤压和不断的风雨侵蚀形成了一片灰黑色的变质石林由此得名墨石公园。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003402947.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003402947\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003406613.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003406613\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003410843.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003410843\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003421237.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003421237\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003433984.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003433984\"></p>\n<p>贡嘎这座让无数登山者向往的“白色雪山”正是整个横断山脉的最高峰。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003453844.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003453844\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003458775.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003458775\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003503542.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003503542\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304003512138.png\" alt=\"image-20220304003512138\"></p>\n","text":"横断山脉 阿坝：童话世界为“世界生态旅游最佳目的地”的阿坝州平日里，我们在成都遥望四姑娘山。 这次，我们翻过巴朗山，越过垭口亲自站在了她的脚下。在猫鼻梁伫足望去，四座并排的山峰就像四位头戴纱巾的姑娘： 四姑娘山景区由双桥沟、长坪沟、海子沟组成其中以双桥沟的景色最为迷人 白塔与彩林...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":565,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"西财摄记","slug":"西财摄记","count":9,"path":"api/categories/西财摄记.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"秋","slug":"秋","count":5,"path":"api/tags/秋.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" 